Installation Guide
------------------

- pipenv installation
...
    pipenv install git+https://git.divineit.net/shimul/wagtail-hyper-editor.git#egg=wagtailhyper

- Add following to your installed apps in settings.py file
...
    INSTALLED_APPS = [
        .....
        'wagtailhyper',
        .....
    ]

- Then add following to your urls.py file

...
    urlpatterns = [
        .....
        url(r'^hyperEditor/', include('wagtailhyper.urls')),
        .....
    ]

You are good to go!


